title: ETH v1 Update: Raise $GNO collateral cap
body:
Intro: This is a vote to raise the collateral cap of GNO on C.R.E.A.M. ETH v1 market.
Proposal: Listing Committee
Rational: GNO is currently capped out on ETH v1 market.

For: 
Raise collateral cap of $GNO to 51,678 or $1.5M USD. 

Against: 
Do not make any changes to ETH v1 market.
author: 0x81f8CaBe89066d43EB4faFD8E4E5256C102E6E30
